{"tid":1457983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"散水撚機場事後檢討","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:39:28.000Z","uid":32226,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7aaf1782c76e5c79eb7001f9955cd2e33bdfee46","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:42:03.000Z","msg":"平時既我係一個前線滅蛋員，但今日機場聽到話封島乜乜77，帶住女朋友既我想和你們飛真係有d淆，所以提早離開。<br />\n但今日做既野絕對有成效！香港機場癱瘓絕對會傳到去外國，再加上實際取消既航班，不論裝人定裝貨既機，我地既對手香港政府、林鄭、警隊一定有受翻呀爺及各界既壓力。<br />\n我地要達到既目的唔洗一步登天，絕對係一個持久戰。我地需要既係一個時機，到政府都頂唔住既時候就係我地勝利之日。大家冷靜完請繼續檢討、進步<br />\n<br />\n不割席 不篤灰<br />\n不撤不撤<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4f0e01fc9df51d0d9c635fc1facdd5be266fce","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:42:10.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"16cb465461e46341e1a8165fa1dae62c648e988d","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"78d3e4553ee58e697f13cd97e57dadf08df9dce5","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:42:32.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"de4b3058b1eeb5292b94308ccabbe8ff89d17cf3","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"2216b6a25602e4124227c0039b86396400c42b34","tid":1457983,"uid":42141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"cc9afbeb2d806815a0a60e764cd9ea4c7a528034","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:42:54.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"44f0b32e6a1d138d886b2dad8910d64b2f8013ba","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"640af564e3acf726ac41581ba860705046c41b1b","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:43:15.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"be655ada1d742885bf91e121b0b54438f29a9588","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"af3ce1ac8ac2573290387eced6a10a65833f5f52","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:43:37.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d6d0c110301d69ca341aeea79d2d5b8988e2c63f","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ade2a272d519191bbda8ea64e4ce189c68acf7b4","tid":1457983,"uid":36588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"反而今日我覺得錯有錯著<br />\n取消晒d機就走<br />\n唔一定冇開拖就係輸<br />\n利申仲係機場"},{"pid":"f81870070455b5d4ed3db7536de448f23061f7ce","tid":1457983,"uid":280436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"【散 定唔散 都係政府個局入面】<br />\n<br />\n政府<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">操縱緊我地嘅言論</span></span>去<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">分化</span></span>勇武同和理非<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果散</span> <br />\n就發表大量<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌撚散水狗</span></span></span>嘅言論<br />\n馬後砲<br />\n指責班合理擔心安全嘅和理非<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">be water</span></span>係大家一直以來重視嘅嘢<br />\n根本勇武唔會怪責<br />\n可見係政府故意引起割席<br />\n<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\">唔散</span><br />\n警察真係做嘢<br />\n就會湧現和理非怪責勇武嘅言論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一切 都係政府設下嘅套路！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日真係有取消/延誤航班 <br />\n警察真係有佈防 而且有機會用得到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但真正目的並非實質行動<br />\n而係分化大家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最近安插臥底係前線同樣<br />\n都有一層目的係為左令尼場運動嘅參與者<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自行瓦解</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大量網軍混入連登，Facebook，telegram<br />\n散播謠言<br />\n令大家<span style=\"color: red;\">質疑</span>盟友嘅可信性<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">互相猜忌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家千奇唔好中政府嘅詭計</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">謹記 不分化 不割席</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢嘅陰濕招數 我地只要團結 一定搵到方法破解"},{"pid":"022307834810b9076486a51ce30826a44a5189b5","tid":1457983,"uid":154634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:45:01.000Z","msg":"唔好有成功感<br />\n飛機delay猶如食生菜<br />\n你話一日有航班cancel哂係咪好大件事<br />\n一定唔係<br />\n要吸收失敗既教訓<br />\n下次要散要留都唔好係因為未fc既野影響"},{"pid":"6b32d884aec64b0244bcee126d09fe57f3d685ca","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ade2a272d519191bbda8ea64e4ce189c68acf7b4","tid":1457983,"uid":36588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"反而今日我覺得錯有錯著<br />\n取消晒d機就走<br />\n唔一定冇開拖就係輸<br />\n利申仲係機場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:47:31.000Z","msg":"無錯！對手雖然唔洗疲於奔命 但已方完全無損兵折將 我地既人每一位都係最珍貴！但我地都叫做到癱瘓機場<br />\n五大訴求雖未達成 但壓力係一直比緊政府<br />\n各位請定必繼續堅持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36ab53be86ca16e6ab6112a173a0970e61e1f26","tid":1457983,"uid":183194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"日日佔機場就有用，一兩日政府彩你都有味，仲記唔記得2014佔左幾個月都係得個吉<br />\n<br />\n星期一佔到星期七，多勞多得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b8495e73c54cd9f963811827bb5dc320bf2d50","tid":1457983,"uid":21920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"緊記<br />\n不要自我分化<br />\n不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好再鬧大家散水黨 留低黨<br />\n<br />\n走唔走既係成果留一樣<br />\n大家唔洗自我分化<br />\n因為一次事件指責自己人係唔抵<br />\n大家要清醒冷靜<br />\n<br />\n萬變不離其宗<br />\n對方只會令到大家指責自己人<br />\n大家團結<br />\n唔好互鬧了<br />\n<br />\n就算係自己人蠢左信假消息都唔好指責<br />\n<br />\n團結<br />\n唔好指責中伏既人<br />\n問題不是訊息傳遞<br />\n是訊息真偽<br />\n<br />\n團結不互鬧<br />\n<br />\n事後不要鬧隊友 指責其他人<br />\n<br />\n傷和氣 失信任是大忌<br />\n<br />\n各位要當今次係經驗不論成功與否都要學習"},{"pid":"04a06e7d8efc0f50b83fdb2e3bc30f2b8e3951fb","tid":1457983,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:48:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">讀稿位係陷阱<br />\n讀稿位係陷阱<br />\n讀稿位係陷阱</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推到唔俾佢哋讀到稿！<br />\n<br />\n一定要咁 KEEP住要咁！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>萬人一推所有記者瘋狂插問追問721 811 唔俾仆街政府讀稿政治宣傳！</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457037</a><br />\n<br />\n唔該幫手推個POST"},{"pid":"ff9658f95cd76d0359f162ddada71e7cbaec10b3","tid":1457983,"uid":238275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5270aqx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5270aqx.png&h=8ee06811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推推推推推推 勁推推推推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勿忘721 811</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9e3ef7621b3d4cef0efab39545365b95c67316e0","tid":1457983,"uid":32226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"022307834810b9076486a51ce30826a44a5189b5","tid":1457983,"uid":154634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:45:01.000Z","msg":"唔好有成功感<br />\n飛機delay猶如食生菜<br />\n你話一日有航班cancel哂係咪好大件事<br />\n一定唔係<br />\n要吸收失敗既教訓<br />\n下次要散要留都唔好係因為未fc既野影響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"係，我地要做既係檢討點樣更有成效 更直接。"},{"pid":"075beb392753de4a4dedc3d94e2f9e61640d3693","tid":1457983,"uid":222581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"雨傘式估機場<img src=\"/